high_descs: Walk to the end of the island bar, turn right and walk to the stove on your left.
Take the drinking glass out of the microwave above the stove.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Put the glass in the sink, rinse it off, and take it back out of the sink.
turn around and walk back to the microwave.
Put the glass in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean drinking glass in the microwave.

high_descs: Grab the glass out of the microwave
Turn right and go to the sink
Wash the glass in the sink and then take it out
Turn around and go to the microwave
Put the glass in the microwave
anns.task_desc: Putting a clean glass in the microwave

high_descs: Turn left, hang a right at the wall, turn right and walk to the stove on the left.
Pick up the clear glass from inside the microwave above the stove and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the sink on the left.
Put the clear glass inside the sink, rinse it for a few seconds and pick it back up.
Turn around and walk to the stove on the right.
Put the rinsed glass inside the microwave above the stove and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed glass in a microwave.
